By BRUCE MCCONACHIE
Both Stephanie Lewis and sorry Nelson
were engagingly innocent as the Girl and Boy.
Although Stephanie‘s Voice was weak and
sorry's stage movement forward, we never
lost interest in their poetry melodrama.
Tom Pope and Milt google, their fathers.
